      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       rid-999-sia-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione record                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-rid-sia-999          .
       rid-999-sia-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Composizione record                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       rid-999-sia-125.
