      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rid-sia-999        to   g-rec                  .
           perform   put-nxt-seq-000      thru put-nxt-seq-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Scrittura record in file [ouf] in formato per   *
      *              * MS-DOS                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   ouf-rec                .
           move      w-rid-sia-999        to   ouf-dat                .
           perform   ouf-fil-wrt-000      thru ouf-fil-wrt-999        .
       rid-999-sia-950.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se errori di scrittura su file             *
